<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Gold2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Gold,</orth> adj. made of gold: <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.296" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 296</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 1.3.92" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 3, 92</bibl>. Figuratively: <emph>his</emph> (the sun's) <cit><quote>g. complexion,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 18.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 18, 6</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>those g. candles,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 1.21.12" default="NO" valid="yes">21, 12</bibl></cit>. <emph>her hairs were</emph> <cit><quote>g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 4.3.142" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 3, 142</bibl></cit>. <emph>in their</emph> (the cowslips') <cit><quote>g. coats,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 1, 11</bibl></cit>.
